The 'sounz' source package comprises the wherewithall to generate several binary
packages as follows:
 sounz            Common package, establishes users, common scripts etc.
 sounz-frontend   Sets up a front-end webserver
 sounz-backend    Comprises the database and backend cronjobs for SOUNZ
 sounz-app        The main application, coded in Ruby on Rails

The package is dedicated to allowing SOUNZ (sounz.org.nz) to maintain all data
pertaining to New Zealand Music, and providing as platform for the public
at large to discover it.